19:09.882 --> 19:11.850
but headed for certain disaster.

19:11.884 --> 19:13.051
Hmm.
Does that sound crazy?

19:13.085 --> 19:14.285
Absolutely.

19:14.320 --> 19:16.421
Well, it's not just the couch.

19:16.455 --> 19:17.922
I'm starting to
feel claustrophobic.

19:17.957 --> 19:19.591
I mean, I wake up
next to Blaine,

19:19.625 --> 19:20.925
I-I go to school
with Blaine,

19:20.960 --> 19:22.927
I come home to Blaine.

19:22.962 --> 19:24.963
I feel like I'm starting
to lose my identity.

19:26.232 --> 19:28.152
Okay, well, stop me if
you don't want my opinion.

19:29.368 --> 19:31.603
Okay, when I first heard
