22:19.698 --> 22:21.933
<i>What am I doing?</i>

22:21.967 --> 22:23.067
<i>Who am I turning into?</i>

22:23.102 --> 22:24.536
<i>I'm losing my authenticity.</i>

22:24.570 --> 22:27.071
<i>How am I gonna be one</i>
