<i>creating an atmosphere</i>

23:25.164 --> 23:27.132
<i>of the quintessential</i>
<i>New York living experience,</i>

23:27.166 --> 23:29.667
<i>but let's be honest,</i>
<i>it's not entirely functional.</i>

23:29.702 --> 23:30.969
<i>Kurt's gonna love this.</i>

23:35.808 --> 23:38.643
Okay, is that one of those
outlines that the police use?

23:38.677 --> 23:40.245
Did somebody die in here?

23:40.279 --> 23:42.647
Sam, this in no way resembles
the shape of a person.

23:42.681 --> 23:43.848
So...?

23:43.883 --> 23:46.117
So, no, no one died in here.

23:46.152 --> 23:47.752
What did you do to your hair?!

23:47.787 --> 23:50.588
Oh, well, thanks to you,
I-I-I got it cut.

23:50.623 --> 23:51.990
And then bursting
with my newfound

23:52.024 --> 23:53.158
New York City confidence,

23:53.192 --> 23:55.426
I went out and I booked
my first modeling job!

23:55.461 --> 23:56.628
What?!
Yeah!

23:56.662 --> 23:57.796
That's amazing!
I know!

23:57.830 --> 24:00.732
